---
import { site } from "../data/site";
---

<aside
  class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-volltar-orange/30 bg-volltar-black text-white p-8 md:p-10 spark-glow"
  data-reveal
>
  <div class="absolute top-0 inset-x-0 h-1 spark-bar" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] gap-8 items-center">
    <div class="max-w-xl">
      <p class="text-volltar-orange text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide">Not sure if I do it?</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mt-2 leading-tight">
        If it is not listed, ring or message anyway.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-white/75 mt-3 leading-relaxed">
        The list on this page is a guide, not a limit. Tiling, furniture builds, odd tech jobs, something you are
        not sure who to ask about — describe it and I will tell you straight whether I can help.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/50 mt-3">{site.replyTime}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row md:flex-col gap-3 shrink-0">
      <a
        href={site.phoneHref}
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-volltar-orange px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-volltar-black transition-colors hover:bg-volltar-orange-light"
      >
        Call {site.phone}
      </a>
      <a
        href={site.whatsappHref}
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-white/25 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:border-volltar-orange hover:text-volltar-orange"
      >
        Message on WhatsApp
      </a>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-white/15 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white/80 transition-colors hover:border-white/40 hover:text-white"
      >
        Send a message
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</aside>
